The paper discusses the use of automated machine learning (AutoML) tools, which are commonly used in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and data science (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper evaluates and compares the performance of these tools, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) principles.
